# KiloCode Configuration

## Project Settings

### Indexing
- `indexStrategy`: workspace-files
- `excludePatterns`:
  - node_modules/
  - dist/
  - .git/
  - "*.lock"
  - pnpm-lock.yaml

### Auto Commands
- prebuild: npm install
- pretest: npm run build

### Context
- maxTokens: 100000
- includePatterns: ["src/**/*.ts", "*.md", "commands/**/*.toml", "skills/**/*.md"]

### Modes
Project modes are defined in `.kilocodemodes` file.

## Available Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| npm run build | Build the MCP server |
| npm run start | Start the server |
| npm run dev | Development mode with watch |
| npm run test | Run tests |
| npm run test:watch | Watch mode for tests |
| npm run lint | Lint markdown files |
| npm run format | Format code |
| npm run check | Check and fix issues |

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies (auto runs build)
npm install

# Run tests
npm test

# Start development
npm run dev
```
